1. Leap Year Check
Start
Input year
IF( year % 4 = 0 ) AND ( year % 100 != 0 OR year % 400 = 0) THEN
   Print "LEAP YEAR"
else
   Print "NOT A LEAP YEAR"
End If
Stop

